menuconfig DRIVERS_GNSS_UBLOX
	bool "u-blox GNSS receivers"
	default n
	---help---
		Enable support for a dedicated, self-contained u-blox GNSS driver.

		Unlike the generic "gps" driver, this driver vendors the UBX protocol
		parser in-tree (no PX4-GPSDrivers submodule) and only supports u-blox
		receivers. It is the basis for firmware-update-over-CAN on cannodes.
